sequenceDiagram
   participant Student
   participant FocusTimeSystem
   participant TimerService
   participant Database


   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: End Focus Session Request
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   FocusTimeSystem->>TimerService: Stop Timer
   activate TimerService
   TimerService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Elapsed Time Data
   deactivate TimerService
   FocusTimeSystem->>Database: Store Session Data
   activate Database
   Database-->>FocusTimeSystem: Confirm Save
   deactivate Database
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Display Summary & Session Stats
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem
